			<a class="AuthorLink" href="/user.asp?usr=5129">Cyst</a>&nbsp;<img src=/images/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="272 posts"><img src=/images/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="272 posts">&nbsp;			
